{"tid":532426,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Ferrari 首款 SUV 確定開發中！","createTime":"2018-01-17T23:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T14:37:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"445ac301d6ee2471373d52e1938393fa78f09554","tid":532426,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T23:50:54.000Z","msg":"過去始終堅持超跑傳統的 Ferrari，甚至曾多次表明不會推出四門或休旅車款，但如今也不得不向市場妥協，FCA 集團執行長 Sergio Marchionne 在今年北美車展上透露，休旅車開發已經在進行中，並指出該車型將會是「市面上跑最快的休旅車」，另外還宣布要打造純電動超跑，與 Tesla 一較高下。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/auto/page/2018/01/17/180117-9261-1-GC8hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fauto%2Fpage%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F180117-9261-1-GC8hp.jpg&h=0b6a3ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFCA 集團執行長 Sergio Marchionne 在今年北美車展上透露，休旅車開發已經在進行中，並指出該車型將會是「市面上跑最快的休旅車」。圖為 Ferrari 休旅預想圖。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒《Bloomberg》報導，先前盛傳 Ferrari 將打造原廠代號為 F16X 的品牌首款休旅車，如今終於得到集團執行長 Sergio Marchionne 的肯定答覆，同時也強調就算是休旅車也依然維持 Ferrari 的性能精神，打造出堪比超跑的動力表現，預計明年或後年推出，擔任品牌獲利的重要角色。<br />\n<br />\nFerrari 首款休旅車，根據先前外媒所掌握到的消息，將會與下一代 GTC4Lusso 一同開發，並建構在相同底盤上，而且是採用四人座設定，讓整體空間表現相當寬敞，不過車型上比起死對頭 Lamborghini 的 Urus 小上一些，整體大小比較偏向 Porsche 的 Macan，同時採用 V8 或 Hybrid 複合動力系統。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/auto/page/2018/01/17/180117-9261-2-oCjOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fauto%2Fpage%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F180117-9261-2-oCjOy.jpg&h=2d081431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFerrari 首款休旅車，根據先前外媒所掌握到的消息，將會與下一代 GTC4Lusso 一同開發。圖為 GTC4Lusso。<br />\n<br />\n除了公布 SUV 開發消息以外，Sergio Marchionne 還表示，Ferrari 正準備打造純電動超跑，甚至放話「如果要打造電力推動的超級跑車，Ferrari 絕對會拿下第一名」，同時也預測，2025 年汽車總銷售量中，傳統燃油汽車所佔比例將減至一半以下，逐漸為油電混合車、電動車、燃料電池車所取代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://auto.ltn.com.tw/news/9261/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fauto.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F9261%2F3&d=dYnu1y3uyfz1DBULOnZBSZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=243724b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fauto.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2F9261%2F3&h=a12ba92f\" target=\"_blank\">http://auto.ltn.com.tw/news/9261/3</a>"},{"pid":"6b9cf4cbce3bb3a092d855ca4311b3c29a03a86f","tid":532426,"uid":73,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"法記d 車好越來越醜"},{"pid":"64fb6f0f937576e7a1a19b116c65e6364a5e785d","tid":532426,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b9cf4cbce3bb3a092d855ca4311b3c29a03a86f","tid":532426,"uid":73,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"法記d 車好越來越醜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"係聽高轉引擎聲啫"},{"pid":"a8313b878871f7f627730dfec1d054c0d2a02c1a","tid":532426,"uid":144611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"mola mola <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff536c2a6dd7abbfa2c4d4beacaa47f2eb874cf","tid":532426,"uid":72735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"當一間車廠變成咁 就算幾有錢都冇用"},{"pid":"09c688807662761556da205beca36bb09a912d5a","tid":532426,"uid":121997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"7到"},{"pid":"cbbbd3594312383c5b60caed38dc31433f77fa40","tid":532426,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"有D似波子"},{"pid":"d34bdd4f74e18d9b99582a26c9ddf131ba5cd1ec","tid":532426,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbbbd3594312383c5b60caed38dc31433f77fa40","tid":532426,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"有D似波子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"宜家d廠將同一個外型增高增肥變大就當新車款, 屌."},{"pid":"4e3d5ab54bbcf90dc50f815b438cba015d9f3b0e","tid":532426,"uid":34971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d34bdd4f74e18d9b99582a26c9ddf131ba5cd1ec","tid":532426,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,